OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud across eastern
OL,6,FCaithness soon dispersing this
OL,7,Fmorning. Otherwise a dry day with some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells. Becmoing very
OL,9,Fwarm, locally hot. Caithness somewhat
OL,10,Fcooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening, one
OL,13,For two thundery shower possible across
OL,14,Fthe northwest. Showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain becoming more
OL,16,Fwidespread overnight in west, but
OL,17,Fdrier in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
