OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FThe west will see showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain, occasioanlly
OL,7,Fheavy. Drier in the east with some
OL,8,Fbrightness along the Moray Firth
OL,9,Fcoast. Brisk west or southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds. Cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,14,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,15,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,16,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
